channel.title: I die on log in?
channel.description:
I fixed my Null problem. Now everytime i log on, i just keep dying and dying. What do I do to fix this? Can someone just explain why this is happening, I can figure out what's causing it after I know why. Thanks.
This is what happens when I try logging in:
[code] DeltaScape Server. Connection from c-24-62-108-156.hsd1.ma.comcast.net:50144 -2 -2 java.lang.ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsException: -2 at Cryption.getNextKey(Cryption.java:49) at stream.createFrame(stream.java:36) at client.setSkillLevel(client.java:16794) at client.loadgame(client.java:9162) at client.run(client.java:15956) at java.lang.Thread.run(Unknown Source) -2 -2 -2 [client-1-Xile owner]: Loading Process Completed [Regular player, lag: 3 ms] ClientHandler: Client null disconnected (c-24-62-108-156.hsd1.ma.comcast.net) Connection from c-24-62-108-156.hsd1.ma.comcast.net:50145 [client-1-Xile owner]: Loading Process Completed [Regular player, lag: 1 ms] Game saved for player Xile owner ClientHandler: Client Xile owner disconnected (c-24-62-108-156.hsd1.ma.comcast.n et) [/code] It says im already logged on, and that. Then i try logging in again, then it works but i start dying.
